      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about the enzymes but i've heard from a few people that as long as you don't take a lot at once it's totally fine. like, if i just take a tiny amount of the extract once a day, is that really going to cause serotonin syndrome? it feels like such a huge risk for just a little bit of extra help while i'm studying. i just really need something to take the edge off tonight.",
